Constructor for the class resDating

resDating.Rd

Constructor for the class resDating

Usage

resDating(
  dt,
  phy,
  algo = "Unknown",
  model = "poisson",
  rate = 10,
  relax = 0,
  rootdate = NA
)

Arguments

dt

Dated phylogeny

phy

Undated phylogeny (may be rooted or not)

algo

Algorithm used for dating

model

Model used for dating

rate

Clock rate used for dating

relax

Relaxation parameter used for dating

rootdate

Date of the root inferred by dating

Value

Object of class resDating
